Description:    Exchange news articles between a local Cnews or INN spool 
		and an external NNTP server.
		Will connect to the remote server and delivers outgoing
		articles using the POST command. Will then start fetching
		new news using the STAT and ARTICLE commands.
		Provides the NNTP capabilities required for small	 
		news spools on installations with NNTP access only 
		through limited ISP accounts. 
		Full error recovery and logging. Beta version.
Keywords:	NNTP, Cnews, INN, news, post
Author: 	Egil Kvaleberg <egilk@sn.no>
Maintained-by:	author
